    <p>I will list some of the notable syntax.</p>
    <h5 id="codeblock"><a href="#codeblock">Codeblock</a></h5>
    <p>Codeblock are fenced by ```</p>
    <pre>{`\`\`\`code-language
code content
\`\`\``}</pre>

    <p>
      There are options to make codeblock more informational. Those options are all optional. If you don&#39;t need, you
      can omit it.
    </p>
    <p>Here are the example:</p>
    <pre>{`\`\`\`js
\/\/\/ title: Title
\/\/\/ lineStart: 0
\/\/\/ hlLines: 0-1, 3
\/\/\/ showLineNumber
\/\/\/ diff
line1
line2
line3
line4
+ line5
- line6
\`\`\``}</pre>

